{
  "stem": "21786.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I am together with brother Hans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I am expected-- I'm expecting that within in the next couple of days I'll be also with Uncle Otto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Please send parcels to the address below.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was some address.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We looked at it and says, Uncle Otto died 10 years ago.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What's happening?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Hans is going probably bonkers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Must be, I mean, so bad if they don't have enough to eat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the translation was quite clear cut.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I realized this means only one thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This means death.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It means the destruction.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I started to look at that point for something that I would be protected from being put into the transport.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got myself into a training as a male nurse.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They created there a small hospital for Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They are bringing Jews from all part of Bohemia and Moravia, mostly old people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Old people-- most were 20 years younger than I am now.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when you are 16 or 17 or 18, everybody's old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we got six weeks training, and I was a nurse.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I knew how to give injections, intravenous injections, how to cut and dress people, how to do all kinds of changing this and similar, which helped me when I became finally a physician.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I realized when I put down ss enema, soap suds enema, that it means something else, that it doesn't mean only the order, that somebody has to do it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But as such I was protected.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I had also a pass by which I could take a street car, which was permitted only for certain Jews on the back platform of the-- of the street car.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
